headline: Humana Board Declares Payment of Quarterly Dividend to Stockholders
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., February 20, 2025--Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM) announced today that its Board of Directors has declared a cash dividend to stockholders of $0.885 per share payable on April 25, 2025 to stockholders of record as of the close of business on March 28, 2025.
